NAME
	arrayp - test if a variable is an array

SYNOPSIS
	int arrayp(mixed arg)

DESCRIPTION
	Check if 'arg' is an array.

RETURN VALUE
	Returns 1 if 'arg' is an array, 0 otherwise.

EXAMPLES
	mixed arg;

	if (!arrayp(arg)) {
	   write("Error.\n");
	}

SEE ALSO
	afun/arrayp, afun/dump_value, afun/floatp, safun/fmt_time,
